      "id": "d491a379-4ee9-49f6-8acb-d70fcfeaa93d",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Social Media Upload Sub-Workflow\n\n**Input payload from parent workflow:**\n```\n{\n  source: 'clickup' | 'sheet',\n  source_id: '<task_id or row_id>',\n  accounts: ['arya instagram', 'arya youtube', 'arya linkedin'],\n  reel_url: '<google drive share url>',\n  cover_url: '<google drive share url>',\n  caption: '<pre-written or empty string>',\n  title: '<video title>'\n}\n```\n\nPlatforms: Instagram Reels, YouTube Shorts, LinkedIn Video\nCredentials: Named in n8n exactly as account name\nAI Caption: Auto-generated if caption field is empty\nStatus writeback: Updates ClickUp task or Google Sheet row",
        "height": 416,
        "width": 616
